</P>
<P>
   LIEBERMAN-HILLARY _ Now that Sen. Joseph Lieberman has been
tapped to be Al Gore's running mate, Hillary Clinton is hoping her
Senate campaign in New York can get a boost from her Connecticut
neighbor, especially among Jewish voters. About 800
</P>
</TEXT>
