lexicon of late. Just this week, even the venerable Wall Street
Journal used it in an editorial, calling Joseph Lieberman ``a
political grown-up who takes ideas seriously.'' If certain
politicians are ``grown-ups,'' what does that make the others?
About 700
</P>
