<SLUG> BC-HEARST-NEWS-BUDGET-HNS </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Tuesday, Aug. 8, 2000 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Editors &LR;  &QL;
