<P>
   TRAVEL
</P>
<P>
   GETAWAY-NCMOUNTAINS _ Visitors to Lake Lure, nestled in the
foothills of the Blue Ridge Mountains of North Carolina, are
impressed to learn that the pristine 1,500-acre lake and
surrounding area doubled for the Catskills in New York State in the
1987 film ``Dirty Dancing.'' But the real story of how one man`s
dream to build an upscale reosrt was dashed by the Depression is
far more dramatic than any movie. (Thrasher, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 35.
</P>
