<HEADLINE>
EDITORS: HAVE YOU SEEN THESE STORIES?... 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; (These excellent ``separate-buy'' articles are distributed by the
New York Times Syndicate.) &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (To publish these articles, they must be purchased from the New
