<HEADLINE>
DECISION 2000 VOTER'S GUIDE TO THE TWO CANDIDATES
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  c. 2000 Houston Chronicle
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR; Candidate: &UR;  &LR; Vanessa
</P>
<P>
   Vital statistics: &UR;  &LR; $19.99, at www.Getsetclub.com. Comes with
Victory for Vanessa campaign kit.
</P>
<P>
   Affiliation: The Surprise Party
</P>
<P>
   Official slogan: ``She's seen the world. She knows the world.
She's ready to lead the world.''
</P>
<P>
   Favorite color: Bright neon yellow (her most recent pedicure.)
</P>
<P>
   Best feature: Realistic proportions and two feet she can
actually stand on.
</P>
<P>
   Background: Journalist, investment banker, scientist and beauty
salon owner.
</P>
<P>
   Agenda: Opposes ``pink prefabricated prescriptions for play.''
Supports ``toys that nourish the brain of a child by stimulating
curiosity, critical thinking and creativity.''
</P>
<P>
   Favorite campaign quote: ``It's not which party you are in. It's
the party you are at.''
</P>
<P>
   &UR;
</P>
<P>
   &LR; Candidate: Barbie
</P>
<P>
   Vital statistics: $19.99, exclusively at Toys 'R' Us. Also
available in African-American and Latina (same outfit.) Comes with
campaign posters, a big hairbrush, a Girls Bill of Rights, and a
red-hot inaugural ballgown. Web site: www.barbie.com.
</P>
<P>
   Affiliation: The Girls Party
</P>
<P>
   Official slogan: To define the ``important issues on the minds
of young girls across the country.''
</P>
<P>
   Favorite color: Pink, obviously.
</P>
<P>
   Best feature: A perky, upbeat personality.
</P>
<P>
   Background: More than 75 careers in 41 years, including fashion
model, ballerina, veterinarian, stewardess, teacher, cowgirl, ice
cream vendor, Indian princess, astronaut, and most recently,
Olympic champion swimmer.
</P>
<P>
   Agenda: Wants girls to talk to adults ``about things on TV that
confuse'' them, try new things in ``math and science,'' and
practice sports skills they are ``least confident'' doing.
</P>
<P>
   Favorite campaign quote: ``Remember: real women sweat, get dirty
and survive bumps and bruises!''
</P>
<P>
   X X X END OF STORY
